Description:
ONLY 400sqm BLOCK LEFT IN POINT COOK ! MUST SECURE !!! Titled Land in Upper Point Cook for your Dream Home!
Dont miss out on your opportunity to buy this excellent block of 400sqm (approx) land in the most popular Upper Point Cook. A block of land this with 12.5m frontage & 32m depth means you can build your dream home, and still have plenty of space for a beautiful outdoor entertaining area, and room for the kids to run around and play.
Upper Point Cook is the best positioned estate west of Melbourne, with everything you and your family need.
Nestled in the established suburb of Point Cook, this masterplanned community offers the perfect place for families to grow in space and comfort.
Eventually, around 2,000 families will call Upper Point Cook home, along with 14 hectares of open space, parks and playgrounds, walking trails, cycling paths and a future neighbourhood park.
One of the most impressive features of Upper Point Cook is the abundance of open space. There are stunning parks and wetlands throughout, contributing to 14 hectares of open space within the community. And you can make the most of all this outdoor space with amenities such as playgrounds, cycling tracks and walking paths.
For families, there are also two proposed child care centres within the estate.
Youll also be just a five minute drive from the Point Cook town centre, close to primary and secondary schools and have a direct connection to the Princes Freeway via Sneydes Road
Don't miss this opportunity call INDER on 0413 200 235 !

Description:
The Pinnacle of Indulgence and Splendour.
Strikingly presented, impeccably proportioned and flawlessly kept is this 4.5 year old (approx.) Carlisle built sensation! Combining remarkable open plan living quarters with a supreme combination of an indoor and outdoor luxury extravagance.
This is a home that solidifies the perfect first impression, up the exposed aggregate concrete driveway, featuring low maintenance front garden, double car remote garage with internal access, and side gate access for your convenience. The grand double door entry opens this luxury home comprising of high ceilings, oozing space and style, offering a true replication of resort style living. Beginning with a spacious study and / or home office, grand formal lounge space and opening to the expansive well-equipped kitchen with 40mm waterfall stone bench tops, stainless steel oven and dishwasher, huge walk in pantry, additional overhead cupboards, glass splashback and a richness of both cooking and bench top space for the chef of the home!
Adjoining to the lavish kitchen is the large sun drenched dining and family room, flowing to the stunning outdoor alfresco space with outdoor café style blinds, overlooking superbly manicured rear gardens. Step outside and experience a tranquil oasis of established surroundings, making this the perfect home for family entertaining inside and out all year round!
Up the extra wide staircase where high ceilings continue is a very large rumpus room space for the kids, as well as four generous sized bedrooms, with master retreat being a glimpse of a hotel suite including spacious walk in robes and ensuite bathroom with dual vanities and oversized shower. Remaining 3 bedrooms all feature walk in robes and an additional bedroom conveniently located downstairs across from the central bathroom with downstairs shower and includes BIR.
Additional features include, stunning plantation shutters, 18 solar electricity panels, evaporative cooling and ducted heating, double car remote garage with internal access, quality window furnishings, security alarm system and security cameras, as well as a spacious laundry with an abundance of storage for the growing family!
Situated in the prestigious Featherbrook estate and zoned to Featherbrook P-9 College, within close commute to shopping facilities, childcare and medical centres, easy freeway access and a short commute to the Point Cook Town Centre and Williams Landing train station.

Description:
Great Opportunity To Secure This Family Home In The Sought After Harpley Estate.
Located a short 10 minute drive to Werribee's town center & only a 35 minute (approx) drive to Melbourne CBD this five bed, two bath, two car newly built masterpiece is perfect for the growing family, first home buyer or investor alike. Built with the finest materials in the lovely suburb that is Werribee, this freshly built home has size, stature, and room to grow. Walk on the driveway, past the newly matured front gardens to find bedrooms one, two & three to your right. With carpeted floors, roller blinds, central heating and built in wardrobes this property has all the comforts of home. A centralized bathroom can be found in between these rooms that has all the modern amenities including a bath and floor to ceiling tiles. As you continue down the hallway you come to the master bedroom, with being over 11m2 in size (not including the WIR) you're treated with size, ensuite & walk in wardrobe. To your left you have the centerpiece of the property, an enormous kitchen living & dining. With waterfall stone bench tops, 900mm appliances, abundant amounts of storage, central heating, LED downlights & roller blinds. To your left there is another lounge, this separate living area can be used as a large study, rumpus room or family area. Step into the backyard to find a large alfresco area with a hardwired gas line (perfect for the BBQ/outdoor heating) freshly landscaped backyard & ample amounts of room for a dog, kids or entertaining. Family was very much kept in mind when building this property, may that be the couple wanting to grow, the family of three soon becoming the family of four or the investor wanting a strong yield. 6 Fairhall Ave may be exactly what you've been looking for.

First home buyers & Investors
Lifein Real Estate proudly presents this young & vibrant family entertainer, Located in Harpley estate just 3km from the Werribee CBD and 30km south west of Melbourne.

Description:
Superbly Spacious in Saltwater Coast
LJ Hooker Point Cook presents 18 Silverbay Avenue, Point Cook. Nestled in the esteemed Saltwater Coast Estate and delivering the very best of modern living, this sleek and contemporary family home awaits your inspection. Spanning two spacious stories, this immaculate residence offers three living zones, three bedrooms plus study, two bathrooms, double car accommodation and a dazzling alfresco. Within easy reach of local shops, schools, parklands and transport, this home is perfectly suited to both families and professionals.
- Boasting 30 squares (approx.) of internal living, this magnificent residence begins with a formal lounge room, flanked by windows and filled with natural light. Currently well-utilized as a games room, this generous space is versatile and brilliantly functional. Venturing further inside, the expansive open plan family and meals zone is revealed, complete with timber look laminate flooring and split system air conditioning.
- Embodying integrated living, the alfresco follows the main roof line, with glass stacker doors ensuring a seamless transition from indoors to out. Perfect for year-round entertaining, this space is finished with timber decking, a ceiling fan and cafe-style roller blinds, enjoying a pleasant outlook over the private green lawn.
- Superbly finished and masterfully designed, the kitchen offers stone countertops including a waterfall island, breakfast bar, glass splash back and stylish pendant lighting. Gleaming stainless-steel appliances include a 900mm gas cooktop, under bench oven, canopy rangehood and dishwasher, surrounded by quality cabinetry and a full-sized pantry.
- The upper level offers a further rumpus room with balcony access as well as three bedrooms and a separate study, each bedroom fitted with built-in-robes and soft carpets underfoot, sharing access to the family bathroom with a spa bath and separate toilet. The luxurious master suite is a palatial retreat, appointed with a walk-in-robe and private en suite.
- This 2012 Simmonds-built home sits upon a corner block, with low maintenance landscaped gardens front and rear including apple, nectarine, peach and pear trees.
- Additional appointments include a double remote-control garage with internal access, an internal laundry, downstairs powder room, split system air conditioning, downlights and roller blinds throughout.
The master planned Saltwater Coast Estate is home to quality residences, and offers access to the lifestyle center, with pool, tennis courts, function room and cafe. An abundance of neighborhood amenities includes quality schools, such as St Mary of the Cross Catholic Primary School, Alamanda K-9 College and Lumen Christi School Point Cook. Local attractions include Silverbay Avenue Park and playground, Point Cook Coastal Park, Saltwater Coast Crocodile Park and Saltwater Community Centre, while public transport options include the nearby Williams Landing station and well-serviced bus routes.
Note. All stated dimensions are approximate only. Particulars given are for general information only and do not constitute any representation on the part of the vendor or agent.

Description:
Sensational Space and Style for the Whole Family!
Free-flowing, instantly inviting and filled with natural light over 2 levels of luxury, this supersized 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom and extra powder room family home positively radiates with 3 far-reaching living areas and main bedrooms on both floors. Superbly set in the heart of Featherbrook Estate, make the most of a fast-growing neighbourhood with lush parkland and wetlands directly across the road.
A genuine feeling of space will inspire with a versatile home cinema that could easily double as a work-ready home office or relaxed formal lounge. Drenched in layer upon layer of natural light, spacious open-plan living and dining is complemented by a sleek stone-finished kitchen boasting an inviting, L-shaped island bench, walk-in pantry and high-end appliances including a dishwasher. These quality appointments ensure comfort levels are at an absolute premium with everything at your fingertips.
Facing north at the rear of the property, there is an inclusive harmony between the indoor and outdoor spaces with a fully enclosed sunroom deck, effortlessly opening up via well-placed sliding glass. This private and peaceful place is ideal for entertaining on any chosen scale, fabulously framed by a landscaped, low-upkeep garden with a paved perimeter.
All 5 bedrooms are impressively staged, sized and robed, serviced by a trio of deluxe bathrooms, the family-sized bathroom showcasing a bath. The upstairs main bedroom offers concealed walk-in robes and a private balcony with a commanding parkland and wetlands panorama.
Enriched by meticulous attention-to-detail, special features include a wide-reaching upstairs retreat, the thoughtful addition of a powder room on ground-floor level, a separate WC on the first floor, large laundry, a number of integrated storage solutions throughout, and a remote-controlled 2-car garage with internal/external access. Further appeal is boosted by ducted heating plus a gas-fuelled open fireplace, recessed LED down-lighting, and a stylish front timber-topped deck for relaxed parkside living.
Convenience is covered with nearby first-class amenities and attractions embedded in the family-focused community. So close to Boardwalk Boulevard and the Sneydes Road freeway interchange, walk to Featherbrook Shopping Centre, Featherbrook Reserve, Featherbrook College, Featherbrook Community Centre, and bus transport to Williams Landing trains. This special Point Cook property is sure to be hotly contested, so do not miss out!

So close to Saltwater Community Centre, Creative Garden Early Learning, Sanctuary Lakes Shopping Centre, Homestead Senior Secondary College and the 497 bus route to Williams Landing city-bound trains, this value-packed gem will not last long!

Description:
A Rare Incredible Beauty.
Be impressed by the unique quality and sophistication presented in this 4 bedroom home situated in a prominent location. You will enjoy the position of this property, set nearby Shopping Centre's, public transport and ideal access to freeway.
Set on approximately 613m2 of land, absolutely stunning and offering separate living areas suitable for the whole family, this home includes a large formal lounge room, kitchen, meals / large family area that opens up to the alfresco entertaining area with extended pergola plus rumpus room. Kitchen with upgraded stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops, lots of cupboards space and a huge walk in pantry.
Master bedroom with retreat / study area, his and her walk in robes that offers great storage and is not easily found. Ensuite is complete with shower, vanity and toilet. 3 further bedrooms all complete with built in robes and central bathroom.
Additional extras include ducted heating and 2 split systems, high ceilings with ceiling fans, high doors, oversize double remote-control garage with internal and rear access great for a boat, trailer or caravan, quality window furnishings, security shutters all around, manicured front and rear gardens.
Positioned perfectly and only a short distance away from Stella Maris Catholic Primary School and Point Cook College, child care centre, parks, the Boardwalk shopping precinct, freeway access and Point Cook town centre.

Description:
!!! A Family Treasure Trove !!!
Bal Real Estate proudly presenting you this spectacular home that embraces a modern feel with a succession of light filled living spaces. With superior fixtures and fittings all through and a great location, this home is the one you have been looking for all this time. The sustainable design of this home offers multiple living areas with a free flowing floor plan which is both practical and aesthetically appealing.
Overflowing with premium features & offering an awe-inspiring floor plan with integrated entertaining areas that families will adore.
This home features 4 bedrooms, Master bedroom includes a spacious walk in robe and En-suite. Three more spacious bedrooms facilitated by spacious central bathroom that includes shower and bath tub with separate toilet. This house encompasses open plan living areas and dining area, incorporating a superb MasterChef kitchen fitted with upgraded 900mm appliances and storage including walk-in pantry.For that added peace of mind, security cameras have been installed around the home capable of capturing and recording high quality video which can be accessed easily via a mobile app on your phone.
Comprising of the following:
-Master with a walk-in robe
-Formal lounge
-Ducted heating, Evaporative cooling,
-40mm stone bench top in kitchen
-Custom shelving for walk-in pantry
-Fully Landscaped front yard and backyard
-Extended Shower in Central Bathroom
-High square-set ceiling, down lights, high doors
-Grand alfresco sitting area
-Double car garage on remote with internal access
-Blinds
-Motion-sensing security cameras around the perimeter of the property
-20mm stone bench top in Laundry and Bathrooms
-Custom shelving in all wardrobes
...and much more...
This Heavenly Abode is situated in Verdant Hill. Verdant hill is covering almost 60 hectares, Verdant Hill's tree-studded parks, peaceful wetlands, vibrant community spaces and lush green play areas are all designed to bring people together. A new sports precinct, with playing fields and tennis courts will be the venue for serious competition and laid-back social activities. More than just a place to live, Verdant Hill is an address that embraces a true sense of neighbourhood. It's a place to create wonderful memories with family and friends - new and old. The parks will set the stage for cultural events and celebrations, while the surrounding towns already welcome you with an array of festivals and entertainment.
Modern and bustling, but retaining a village charm, Tarneit and Truganina offer everything you need to enjoy an easy connected life. Shopping centres, major services and quality schools abound, festivals celebrate diversity and culture, and smooth transport links by road and rail can have you in the city or at the beach within minutes.
Come and view this elevated and elegant family home that's certain to attract an assortment of potential buyers.
Call Bal Amardeep on 0413 870 550 or Kamal Kaler on 0469 332 699 to arrange an inspection as this one won't last long.
